channel.description: Title says it all, I downloaded PimpScape... I got stuck at the router bit in Mod Taharoks guide.. I don't care if it's no-ip or hamachi I just wanna' make a god damn server! Help... :|[br][size=1]Posted on: February 23, 2007, 11:49:46 PM[/size][hr]Or is someone could give me a link to a server that doesn't need any programs my friend used the new pimpscape...
